This is one freaking crazy map, With 20 players a team, Only 4 rooms, and hallways in between, You'll experience extreme-fast paced action!!

Tip: Most guns can peirce these walls, So if an enemy runs out of sight, Spamming the walls may net you a kill, or two... Or maybe 5 if you're lucky :D

This is the Saturday, 25 November 2006 version, A much better improvement from first version where you would hit your head jumping, and all props removed from both spawns so you can actually run around now! 

I won't be updating this version, But there may be sequels of HallwayBlitz so stay tuned!

PS: HallwayBlitz2 is has been released in some places but here, I will be updating that version by getting rid of the props in those spawns as well.

This is map32 of DooM 2, called Grosse.  It's a good layout for an arena type fy map.

All the textures used are the exact ones from the DooM map, recreated with normal maps.  And the map itself is drawn exactly to scale as the DooM map as well, along with all the same secrets in the DooM map.  So if you know youre way around this small map already, you may just have an advantage.

Hope ya guys/girls like it!

I'd also like to give some credit for hitmanx who gave me the idea for this map in the first place.

This map is a Fight Yard (fy) map.
You play on two sides, which are shielded from each other by a wall.
In the wall there are small holes where you can swim in.
After 40 sec. the water level decreases and the bulkhead rises.
On the bottom of the map there is built a small complex where the Ts and CTs can fight further if they are still not dead. Have fun.

This map is composed of a straight road 
and china buildings. 

Player who are proficient at sniper shooting 
will like this map.

Map characteristics:

- 32 spawn points
- weapons are available without the buyzone
- map contains both outside and inside locations
- compiled with HDR
- perfectly playable with BOTs


ZIP contains:

fy_greenbright.bsp [the map itslef]
fy_greenbright.nav [navigation meshes for bots]


To Install:

Extract contents of the .zip file into your CS:Source directory (e.g. C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\[YOUR STEAM USERNAME]\counter-strike source), path may vary, depending on the system you use.


Hope you'll like it.

Fy_gow_gridlock is a map based on the multiplayer map on Gears of War.

This map is currently in Beta stage!
